title: Dinosaurs (Tribute to Blockchai) By Saint Ignatius of Cyberspace
description: This single is about the revolutionizing technology known by the name blockchain, as made popular by the innovative and disruptive cryptocurrency bitcoin, and summarizes the history, timeline, public view, surrounding stigma, and future of the world renown digital money mogul. Furthermore, this song draws upon some of the challenges which bitcoin has experienced and addresses the current financial climate and environment as being ancient, outdated, and due for replacement by blockchain. This track is dedicated to bitcoin, blockchain, and was written, performed, and mixed by a tech geek for all the tech geeks around the world. Great minds think alike. Lyrics Written and Performed by: Saint Ignatius (Also Known As St. Ignatius of Cyberspace) Music used: Ever Felt pt.1 by Otis McDonald Licensed under Creative Commons Attribution 3.0 Song Mixed and Mastered by: Saint Ignatius of Cyberspace http://www.saintignati.us http://www.apptyze.com Binary Gospell EP (The Album): The Binary Gospell EP is a Raspberry Pi project currently in the works and is a hip-hop studio album by Saint Ignatius of Cyberspace, expected to be fully completed and launched by end of 2018. The album will focus on delivering a sound that resonates with the uplifting soulful and funky '90's era sample based conscious hip-hop with an overtone of live instrument play (ex. The Roots), while the lyrical content and rhymes will be driven by principles of lyricism which will cover a wide range of topics belonging to the lifestyle of a typical millennial geek (ex. Saint Ignatius of Cyberspace). BTC: 1Pu1ymV3gb622E3GcTRPt2YZmomMzKyHES ETH: 0x700f358098df656c57abecb2c61f664efdd1f97d LTC: LTbXoG7UXaLhJCA1dbyoCgQvc2mSR67eTk
